  "body": "### Description\n\nFrom Dekorate 2.9.0 (unreleased yet), Dekorate will include a new module to generate Helm artifacts (see https://dekorate.io/docs/helm).\r\nDekorate is already used by Quarkus to generate OpenShift and Kubernetes artifacts, so it would be great to have the Quarkus Helm extension to also generate the Helm artifacts.\r\n\r\nInterested in this extension, please +1 via the emoji/reaction feature of GitHub (top right).\n\n### Configuration suggestion\n\nDekorate Helm module is fully configurable via properties. The Quarkus Helm extension would look like as:\r\n\r\n```\r\nquarkus.helm.name=myChart\r\nquarkus.helm.version=1.0.0-SNAPSHOT\r\nquarkus.helm.description=Description of my Chart\r\n```\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_",
